Adadin masu kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) ya karu cikin sauri a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Adadin masu kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) a cikin ƙasashen Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Burtaniya ya nuna cewa, duk da bambancin da ke tsakanin ƙasashe, cutar ta COVID-19 tana yaduwa cikin sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Dangane da abin da ya faru a Italiya, jihohi, asibitoci da cibiyoyin kula da gaggawa dole ne su kasance cikin shiri don karɓar adadi mai yawa na masu cutar COVID-19 waɗanda za a buƙaci kulawa, musamman dangane da kula da marasa lafiya masu wahala.
A ranar 31 ga watan Disamba, 2019, an samu wasu mutane da suka kamu da cutar sankara da ba a san dalilin da ya sa ba a kai su birnin Wuhan, lardin Hubei, na kasar Sin.
A ranar 9 ga Janairu, 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin Cutar Sin ta ba da sanarwar kamuwa da sabon coronavirus wanda yanzu ake kira SARS-CoV-2.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, cutar da ke haifar da kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 ana kiranta cutar coronavirus (COVID-19).
A halin yanzu, shaidar ta nuna cewa kusan kashi 80% na mutanen da ke dauke da COVID-19 suna da ƙananan cututtuka, ko kuma cututtukan numfashi da ke da alaƙa da cutar, kuma yawancin suna warkewa.
A cikin kashi 14 cikin dari na masu cutar, COVID-19 na haifar da rashin lafiya mai tsanani wanda ke buƙatar asibiti yayin da sauran kashi 6 cikin dari ke buƙatar kulawa a cikin ɗakunan gaggawa.
Yawan mutuwar asibiti na COVID-19 ya kai kashi 4%.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun bincika yanayin yawan mutanen da ke kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa a cikin Tarayyar Turai/EEA da Burtaniya (UK) kuma mun kwatanta shi da lardin Hubei, China.
Mun kuma kwatanta adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a yanzu a cikin EU/EEA da UK da Italiya daga 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris 2020.
Masu cutar COVID-19 a EU/EEA da UK
Bayan kasar Sin, COVID-19 ya ci gaba da yaduwa zuwa wasu kasashe kuma cutar ta COVID-19 ta bazu a duk duniya kamar yadda ta faru a kasar nan.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Darakta Janar na Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
A cikin fitowar Eurosurveillance 2020 na 5 ga Maris, Spiteri da abokan aikinsa sun sanar da adadin mutanen da suka fara tabbatar da cutar COVID-19 a Turai bisa ga ma'anar WHO.
A cikin EU/EEA, Faransa ta gano mutane uku na farko da suka kamu da cutar a ranar 24 ga Janairu, 2020 a cikin mutanen da suka dawo daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
Ya zuwa ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an samu karuwar cutar COVID-19 a kasashe 30 na EU/EEA da kuma Birtaniya, wanda ya kai ga samun karuwar cutar ta COVID-19 39,768 da mutuwar 1,727, wanda 17,750 da mutuwar 1,441 a Italiya kadai.
Gano yawan masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 da kuma yadda take yaduwa a duniya
A Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC), an ba da bayanan COVID-19 na kasashe a duniya daga tushen amintacce kamar Ma'aikatar Lafiya, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa da na yanki da WHO, wanda ake sabuntawa kowace rana da karfe 8:00.
An yi amfani da wannan bayanin don nazarin yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya, da kuma kwatanta shi da Italiya.
Don nuna halin da ake ciki na COVID-19, mun tattara adadin COVID-19 na kwanaki 14, don haka muna mai da hankali kan yanayin yaduwar COVID-19 a cikin kowace ƙasa ta EU / EEA da Burtaniya daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Mun kuma nuna adadin masu kamuwa da cutar a kowace kasa a ranar 15 ga Maris 2020 da karfe 8:00 na safe idan aka kwatanta da Italiya tsakanin 31 ga Janairu da 15 ga Maris 2020.
Matsayi na COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK
Gabaɗaya, jimlar adadin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya sun kasance iri ɗaya a cikin kwanaki 14 kamar yadda yake a lardin Hubei na China (Hoto 1).
Gabaɗaya a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya, adadin waɗanda suka kamu da COVID-19 ya fara ƙaruwa a ranar 21 ga Fabrairu sannan ya ƙaru sosai a ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020 (Sarin bayani).
Wannan ya samo asali ne daga karuwar adadin wadanda suka kamu da cutar a Italiya, amma duk sauran kasashen EU/EEA da Burtaniya sun sami karuwar adadin wadanda suka kamu da cutar ta COVID-19 (Sarin bayani).
Shafi na 2 ya nuna kimanin adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19, a cikin EU/EEA da UK da Italiya daga 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Ya nuna cewa, a ranar 15 ga Maris, karfe 8:00, sauran ƙasashe 15 na EU/EEA da Burtaniya sun riga sun nuna jimillar adadin waɗanda suka kamu da cutar kamar Italiya a cikin makonni 3 da suka gabata ko ƙasa da haka.
Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 zai tashi nan ba da jimawa ba a EU/EEA da kuma Burtaniya.
Canje-canje a cikin adadin mutanen da ke kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 ya nuna cewa cutar tana yaduwa a cikin sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Wannan duk da cewa akwai matakan gwaji daban-daban a cikin kasashe, matakan kiwon lafiya na canzawa, ma'anar kamuwa da cuta na iya bambanta daga ƙasa zuwa ƙasa, da kuma ka'idoji daban-daban don zaɓar waɗanda za a gwada su don tabbatar da cutar ta COVID-19, gami da gwajin waɗanda ba su iya yin gwajin ba.
A farkon watan Maris na shekarar 2020, likitocin da ke yankunan da cutar ta addabi a Italiya sun bayyana cewa kusan kashi 10 cikin 100 na masu fama da COVID-19 na bukatar kulawar gaggawa, kuma kafofin yada labarai sun ce asibitocin gaggawa da ke yankunan sun riga sun karɓi adadin da ba za a iya wucewa ba.
Bayanai kan marasa lafiya da suka kamu da COVID-19 da aka kwantar a asibiti ko kuma a cibiyoyin kula da gaggawa a halin yanzu suna samuwa a matakin EU/EEA a halin yanzu kashi 6% da 1% na marasa lafiya ne (bayanai ba a bayyana su ba).
Duk da haka, dole ne a tattara shi sosai don tattara bayanai game da marasa lafiya da ake bi a halin yanzu ta hanyar mai da hankali kan adadin waɗanda suka kamu da cutar da kuma adadin waɗanda suka mutu.
Wani bincike na 2010/11 ya nuna cewa dakunan kula da gaggawa da dakunan kula da marasa lafiya masu saurin zuwa sun bambanta a Turai, daga gado 29.2 a Jamus zuwa 4.2 a kowace mutane 100,000 a Portugal.
Wannan yana nufin cewa ƙasashe na iya samun ƙarin ko ƙasa da kayan aiki fiye da Italiya (suna da gadajen asibiti da marasa lafiya 12.5 ga mutane 100,000 a 2010).
A cikin sabon bayani na shida na saurin binciken ECDC game da COVID-19, an ba da misalai na yawan marasa lafiya da suka wuce matakin kulawa, tare da kimantawa ga kowace EU / EEA da Burtaniya na marasa lafiya na COVID-19 da ke asibiti da kuma kusan kashi 90% na marasa lafiya da suka wuce gado a cikin asibiti.
Tun da yake a yanzu wasu yankuna a cikin EU/EEA da UK suna da yawan masu kamuwa da cutar, kuma asibitoci da cibiyoyin kula da gaggawa suna karɓar mutane daga wani yanki, ya kamata a sami bayanai game da marasa lafiya da gadajen gaggawa a cikin ƙididdigar yanki na 2 (NUTS-2).
Misali na Italiya da kuma yanayin da ke faruwa a wasu ƙasashe ya nuna cewa annobar COVID-19 tana yaduwa cikin sauri a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya.
Saboda haka, ƙasashe, asibitoci da cibiyoyin kula da gaggawa dole ne su shirya don magance ci gaba da kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 a cikin al'umma tare da karuwar adadin masu cutar COVID-19 da ke buƙatar kulawa, musamman dangane da kula da marasa lafiya masu tsanani, kamar yadda yake faruwa a yankunan da ke fama da cutar a Italiya.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a cikin wani bincike na gaggawa na ECDC, yana da mahimmanci a yi amfani da gaggawa da kuma matakan gaggawa na gaggawa don hana yaduwar SARS-COV-2, saboda haka maye gurbin matakan rigakafi da kewaye da zaman gida, saboda hauhawar da ake tsammani na yawan masu kamuwa da cutar na iya hana masu yanke shawara da ma'aikatan asibiti isasshen lokaci don yin nazari, yarda da matakan da ya kamata su ɗauka da kuma aiwatar da su idan ba a dauki matakin farko ba.
Binciken gaggawa na al'amuran zai kuma nuna matakan kiwon lafiyar jama'a da ake ɗauka don rage tasirin cutar.
Akwai wasu 'yan hanyoyi da kasashe za su iya amfani da su don kara inganta matakan da suke dauka don rage yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 da kuma tasirinsa ga bangarorin kiwon lafiya.
Idan ba a yi haka ba, akwai yiwuwar cewa hukumomin kiwon lafiya na sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA za su fuskanci matsalar yawan masu fama da cutar a cikin kwanaki ko makonni masu zuwa.
Cutar cutar kwayar cutar korona ta 2019 (COVID-19), wacce ta haifar da cutar sankarar rai mai saurin kamuwa da cuta ta numfashi (SARS) SARS-CoV-2, ta kashe sama da mutane 3,000 tare da kamuwa da mutane sama da 80,000 a China da sauran kasashen duniya, kuma ta zama bala'i ga al'umma.
Kamar sauran kwayar cutar, SARS-CoV, wanda ya haifar da cutar sankarar bargo (SARS) a dubban mutane a 2003, SARS-CoV-2 na iya yaduwa ta hanyar ƙwayoyin cuta kuma yana da alamun bayyanar cututtuka iri ɗaya.
Amma COVID-19 ba shi da tsanani sosai kuma yana kashe mutane da yawa fiye da SARS duk da cewa yana yaduwa da sauri kuma yana shafar tsofaffi fiye da matasa da kuma maza fiye da mata.
Saboda yawan labaran da ake yi game da wannan sabon cutar, wannan takarda tana ƙoƙari ta samar da cikakken bayani game da wannan batun da ake ci gaba da bincike.
Muna mai da hankali kan mahimman bayanai kamar su ilimin cutar, abin da ke haifar da ita, kwayar cutar da ke haifar da ita, yadda ake ganewa, yadda ake bi da ita, yadda take yaduwa da kuma yadda za a hana ta.
Duk da cewa har yanzu akwai tambayoyi da yawa da za a amsa, muna fatan cewa wannan binciken zai taimaka wajen gano da kuma kawar da wannan cuta mai barazana.
Bikin bazara na ranar 25 ga Janairu, 2020 ya kafa tarihi mai ban mamaki a cikin duk Sinawa waɗanda aka nemi su zauna a gida a duk lokacin hutu da makonni masu zuwa saboda annobar cutar ta sabon kwayar cutar.
Kwayar cutar tana da alaƙa da kwayar cutar korona (CoV) da ta haifar da annobar cutar zazzabin cizon sauro (SARS) a shekara ta 2003; saboda haka Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta sanya mata suna SARS-CoV-2 a ranar 11 ga Fabrairu 2020, kuma yanzu ana kiran cutar da ta haifar da cutar cutar CoV 19 (COVID-19).
Cutar ta fara ne a birnin Wuhan na kasar Sin, kuma ta bazu zuwa kasar da kuma kasashe 50 a duniya.
Ya zuwa ranar 2 ga Maris, 2020, sama da mutane 80,000 ne suka tabbatar da kamuwa da cutar COVID-19, fiye da 40,000 daga cikinsu an warke, kuma sama da mutane 3,000 sun mutu.
WHO ta yi gargadin cewa COVID-19 shine "magabcin duniya na 1" kuma yana iya haifar da tasiri fiye da ta'addanci.
A cewar PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), a cikin kasa da watanni biyu, an buga sama da takardu 200 kan COVID-19 da suka hada da abubuwan da suka shafi kwayar cutar, cutar, asalinta, yadda ake bincikar ta da kuma yadda ake magance ta tun bayan da aka fitar da rahoton farko a ranar 7 ga Janairu 2020 wanda ya bayyana yanayin kwayar cutar da aka gano a cikin marasa lafiya daban-daban.
Wannan bita yana ƙoƙarin taƙaita binciken da aka riga aka yi akan wannan sabon batun kuma ana ci gaba da bincike sosai.
A duk lokacin da zai yiwu, za mu yi ƙoƙarin kwatanta COVID-19 da SARS da sauran cututtukan da ke haifar da CoV, kamar su mura ta Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS, wanda aka gano a shekarar 2012).
Za mu kuma duba darussan da muka koya har zuwa yanzu game da hana yaduwar cutar da kuma gano tushen cutar da kuma wasu tambayoyi masu gaggawa da ba a amsa ba.
Kwayoyin cuta na CoVs, waɗanda aka fi ɗauka a matsayin ƙwayoyin cuta masu saurin kashewa, suna haifar da nau'ikan 4 na mura na yau da kullun a kusan kashi 15%.
Amma, a wannan karni, mun fuskanci nau'ikan CoVs masu saurin kamuwa da cutar sau biyu, SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, wadanda suka haifar da barkewar cutar a China a 2003 da Saudi Arabia a 2012, sannan suka bazu zuwa wasu kasashe da dama inda mutane da dama suka kamu da cutar.
Wannan shine dalilin da ya sa COVID-19 na zamani shine annoba ta uku ta CoV a tarihin ɗan adam.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a hoto na 1.1, an fara gano cutar da ba a san dalilin da ta haifar ba a Wuhan a ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, wanda kuma aka sanar da Hukumar Lafiya ta China.
Bayan kwana bakwai ne aka fitar da takardar bayanin cutar ta CoV.
An samu mutuwar farko a Wuhan a ranar 15 ga Janairu, 2020.
A halin yanzu cutar ta bazu cikin sauri zuwa wasu birane, larduna da ƙasashe makwabta.
A ranar 20 ga watan Janairu, an bayar da rahoton cewa wasu likitoci sun kamu da cutar, wanda a bayyane yake cewa mutane na iya kamuwa da cutar.
A ranar 23 ga watan Janairu, an sanya birnin Wuhan a cikin kwanton bauna kuma an dakatar da dukkan hanyoyin sufuri.
A ranar 24 ga watan Janairu ne aka fara gudanar da binciken asibiti kan cutar, inda aka gano cewa daga cikin mutane 41 da aka tabbatar da cutar, 21 ne kawai suka kai kasuwar ruwa ta Wuhan inda ake zargin cewa cutar ta samo asali ne daga wani dabba da ba a san ko wane irin kwayar cutar ba.
A ranar 30 ga watan Janairu, WHO ta ayyana annobar a matsayin bala'in da ke damun lafiyar duniya.
A lokacin da aka buga wannan rahoton, cutar ta riga ta bazu a duk ƙasar Sin da kuma wasu ƙasashe 50 a duniya (Hoto (Hoto 2).2).
Saboda yadda cutar ke yaduwa cikin sauri, ba shi da sauƙi a san yadda za ta sake dawowa da kuma sakamakon da za ta haifar.
A ranar 11 ga watan Fabrairun 2020, binciken da aka gudanar a cibiyoyi daban-daban kan marasa lafiya 8,866 da suka hada da marasa lafiya 4,021 da aka tabbatar da cutar COVID-19 ya ba da hoto mafi inganci game da yadda annobar ta kasance a shafin yanar gizon (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
Mutane da ke kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 suna da shekaru daban-daban, amma sun fi yawa a tsakanin shekaru 30 zuwa 65.
Kusan rabin (47.7%) na masu kamuwa da cutar sun haura shekaru 50, kuma kaɗan ne a ƙarƙashin shekaru 20, kuma kawai 14 daga cikinsu suna ƙasa da shekaru 10.
Maza sun fi kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 (0.31/100,000) fiye da mata (0.27/100,000).
COVID-19 ya yadu sosai a Hubei da yankuna da ke kewaye da shi.
A matsakaita, daga bayyanar COVID-19 zuwa ganowar cutar ya wuce kwanaki 5 (2-9).
