A gefe guda, kwayar cutar MERS-CoV ta daɗe tana cikin raƙuma.
Waɗannan raƙuman suna da muhimmanci wajen sufuri da kuma samar da nama, madara, ulu da kuma tufafi ga mazaunan yankin.
Sun yaɗu sosai a Gabas ta Tsakiya da Afirka.
Saboda haka, ba za a iya kashe dukkan raƙuma ba don magance cutar MERS, kamar yadda aka yi a kasuwar dabbobi a China don hana yaduwar SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV-2.
Don hana sake barkewar cutar MERS, dole ne a yi aiki mai ƙarfi tare da sauran matakan rigakafi da kuma samar da allurar rigakafin cutar MERS-CoV.
Idan ba mu iya kawar da wannan kwayar cutar ba, za a iya samun sabon nau'in kwayoyin halitta da zai iya haifar da annoba.
