Na biyu, idan kwari ke kaiwa mutane kwayar cutar kai tsaye, ya kamata a nuna yadda mutane ke hulɗa da kwari.
Na uku, idan dabba ta uku tana aiki ne a matsayin dabba mai cin nama, to yaya ta ke hulɗa da nau'ikan dabbobi kamar mutane, da namomin kaza da dabbobi masu rarrafe.
A ƙarshe, idan yawancin dabbobi masu shayarwa da dabbobi masu kiwo suna iya kamuwa da SARS-CoV-2, ya kamata a yi bincike da kuma gano yadda suke kamuwa da cutar.
Ko dai a cikin dabbobi masu shayarwa, dabbobi masu shayarwa ko wasu dabbobi masu shayarwa, ana sa ran cewa SARS-CoV-2 ko kuma kwayoyin cutar da ke dauke da shi za su bayyana a cikin dabbobi masu shayarwa a nan gaba.
Binciken da aka ci gaba a kan waɗannan dabbobi zai bayyana hanyar juyin halittar SARS-CoV-2 a cikin dabbobi, wanda zai taka rawa sosai wajen hanawa da kuma magance COVID-19 a cikin mutane.
Ana buƙatar sabunta ƙa'idodin gwajin COVID-19  waɗanda ake zargi da cutar  waɗanda aka tabbatar da su 
A ranar 6 ga Fabrairu, 2020, ƙungiyarmu ta buga jagororin gaggawa waɗanda suka ƙunshi shawarwari don ganowa da maganin cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (2019-nCoV), kuma jagororin sun ba mu kwarewa da kuma samar da kyakkyawan bayani game da yadda za a magance cutar a duniya.
Koyaya, cutar coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) sabuwar cuta ce, kuma fahimtarmu da iliminmu game da ita suna ƙaruwa a hankali bisa ga bincike da aikin asibiti; don haka hanyoyin bincike da magani suna ci gaba da sabuntawa.
A cikin wannan wasika, mun mayar da martani ga ka'idodinmu kuma mun gabatar da sabbin hanyoyin da za a bi don tantance mai yiwuwa  da wanda aka tabbatar da cutar  bisa ga sabon jagorar bincike da magani na COVID-19 (mataki na bakwai) da kwamitin kiwon lafiya na Jiha na kasar Sin ya fitar.
A watan Disamba na 2019, sabon kwayar cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (2019-nCoV) ta haifar da barkewar cutar, wanda yanzu ana kiranta da sunan cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19) kuma an sanya wa kwayar cutar sunan cutar coronavirus mai saurin numfashi ta 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba ta duniya.
Don magance cutar SARS-CoV-2, ƙungiyarmu ta kafa ƙa'idodin shawarwari na gaggawa kuma an buga su a shafin yanar gizon Cibiyar Nazarin Kiwon Lafiya ta Soja a ranar 06 ga Fabrairu 2020.
Tun da aka fitar da shi, ya burge mutane da yawa.
Amma yana da mahimmanci a fahimci cewa COVID-19 sabon cuta ne, fahimtarmu da iliminmu suna ƙaruwa a hankali bisa ga bincike da aikin likita; saboda haka, hanyoyin bincike da magani suna ci gaba da sabuntawa.
Misali, Jagororin Bincike da Kula da COVID-19 da Kwamitin Lafiya na Jiha na Jamhuriyar Jama'ar Sin (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/) ya bayar, tsakanin 16 ga Janairu, 2020 zuwa 3 ga Maris, 2020, ya fitar da littattafai bakwai da suka hada da wasu sassan da aka gyara.
Yanzu tsarinmu ya karɓi shawarar Zhou da sauransu, waɗanda suka ƙirƙiri tsari mai sauƙi na ƙididdigar ƙwarewar likita.
Aikin su ya kara sabbin hujjoji na zahiri ga manufofinmu kuma ya ba da haske mai amfani game da wannan annoba ta duniya.
Muna goyon bayan waɗannan 'yan'uwa masu ƙwazo kuma muna godiya.
Koyaya, ya kamata a sake sabunta su bisa ga sabbin ka'idoji don ganowa da maganin COVID-19 (Gwaji na bakwai) da kuma sabon bincike.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a littafin na bakwai (3 Maris 2020) tabbatar da cutar da ake zargi dole ne ya dace da ɗayan alamun tarihin cutar da alamun cutar guda biyu don yin cikakken bincike, ko kuma dole ne ya haɗu da alamun cutar guda uku idan tarihin cutar bai bayyana ba:
Tarihin cutar: (1) Tafiya ko zama a Wuhan da kewayenta, ko kuma wasu wuraren da aka gano cutar COVID-19 a cikin kwanaki 14 da suka gabata kafin bayyanar cututtuka; (2) Haɗuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 (tare da gwajin da ke nuna cewa tana da kwayar nucleic acid); (3) Haɗuwa da masu zazzabi ko kuma masu cutar numfashi daga Wuhan da kewayenta, ko kuma wasu wuraren da aka gano cutar COVID-19 a cikin kwanaki 14 da suka gabata kafin bayyanar cututtuka; (4) Haɗuwa da masu cutar da ke da cutar a wani yanki (fiye da mutane 2 da suka sami cutar zazzabi ko kuma marasa lafiya da suka sami cutar numfashi a cikin makonni 2, kamar gida, gida, makaranta, ofis, da sauransu).
Alamun cutar sune: (1) zazzabi ko alamun rashin numfashi; (2) tare da alamun cutar COVID-19; (3) yawan adadin ƙwayoyin jini na farin jini wanda ke nuna yawan ƙwayoyin jini na al'ada, wanda ba ya ƙaruwa ko raguwa a matakin farko.
Binciken wanda aka tabbatar da cutar ya kamata ya dogara ne akan wanda ake zargi da cutar wanda ke nuna ɗayan waɗannan alamun cutar ko kuma wanda ya dogara da jini: (1) gwajin PCR na ainihi wanda ya nuna cutar SARS-CoV-2; (2) jerin kwayoyin cuta masu mahimmanci waɗanda ke nuna alaƙa da sabon coronavirus da aka sani; (3) gano cutar akan takamaiman IgM da IgG a cikin SARS-CoV-2 a cikin gwajin ƙwayar cuta; ko kuma canzawar takamaiman kwayar cutar SARS-CoV-2 daga marasa lafiya, ko ƙaruwa a cikin wani wuri fiye da sau 4 a cikin lokacin warkewa fiye da lokacin cutar.
Mun lura cewa an kara gwajin kwayar nucleic acid ta numfashi ko kuma samfurin jini na lokaci a littafin na biyu (18 ga Janairu 2020) da na uku (22 ga Janairu 2020).
Gano cutar ta hanyar samfurin jini an kara shi a fitowar ta huɗu (27 Janairu 2020) da ta biyar (8 Fabrairu 2020); sannan kuma an kara bayanan jini a fitowar ta bakwai.
Wannan canji ya dogara ne akan ci gaba da bincike na bincike don ingantaccen ganowa na nucleic acid don saurin bincike, da kuma samfurori na numfashi ciki har da samfurin jini, wanda ke ba da damar samfurori daban-daban, da kuma tallafawa shigar da takamaiman kwayoyin cutar cikin tsarin da aka tabbatar.
Bugu da ƙari, akwai alamun da yawa da ke tunatar da mu game da marasa lafiya da ke da alamun rashin lafiya da kuma marasa lafiya.
Saboda haka, ya kamata a sabunta jadawalin Zhou da sauransu, kamar yadda suka rarraba mutumin da ba shi da alamun cutar a matsayin "mai ƙarancin haɗari".
Ya kamata a yi la'akari da tsarin da aka tsara a wasu ayyukan kiwon lafiya da bincike.
A ƙarshe, muna fatan ƙarin tabbaci kai tsaye zai bayyana kuma muna kira ga masu karatu su yi tsokaci.
Game da gwajin "mai yiwuwa" da "an tabbatar da cutar", muna roƙonku da ku bi kuma ku bi sababbin ƙa'idodin ƙasashenku.
Ƙungiyarmu za ta kuma riƙa sabunta ƙa'idodinmu a kai a kai don su taimaka.
Bangladesh ta sanar da sabbin mutane biyar da suka mutu daga COVID-19, wanda shine mafi girma a cikin rana ɗaya
Jiya, Bangladesh ta tabbatar da sabbin mutane biyar da suka mutu daga COVID-19 a wannan ranar.
Wannan shi ne adadin mutane da suka mutu a rana daya sakamakon cutar.
Har zuwa jiya, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka, Cututtuka da Bincike ta Bangladesh (IEDCR) ta ba da rahoton adadin waɗanda suka kamu da cutar, ciki har da 114 da suka kamu da cutar da 33 da suka warke.
Adadin wadanda suka mutu ya kai 17.
A wani rahoto da ya yada a yanar gizo, Daraktan IEDCR, Dr Meerjady Sabrina Flora, ta ce, wadanda suka mutu sun hada da maza hudu da mace daya.
A cewar Dr Meerjady, mutum biyu da suka mutu sun haura shekaru 60, biyu sun haura shekaru 51 zuwa 60 kuma daya ya haura shekaru 41 zuwa 50.
Ya kuma bayyana cewa biyu daga cikin wadanda cutar ta kashe sun fito ne daga birnin Dhaka.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba a ranar 11 ga Maris.
Wani ma'aikacin asibiti ya shaida wa Anadolu, wata jarida mai tasowa a kasar, cewa daya daga cikin wadanda suka mutu shine Jalal Saifur Rahman, Shugaban Hukumar yaki da cin hanci da rashawa ta Bangladesh, wanda ke jinya a asibitin Kuwait Maitree.
A cikin sanarwar bidiyo da aka watsa ta yanar gizo a ranar Lahadi, Ministan Sufuri na Bangladesh Obaidul Quader ya ce an dakatar da zirga-zirgar jama'a fiye da yadda aka tsara har zuwa Asabar.
An shirya wannan dokar ta fara ranar 26 ga Maris kuma ta ƙare ranar Asabar, 4 ga Afrilu.
Ana iya ɗaukar kayan masarufi kamar magani, wuta da abinci.
An gano cutar COVID-19 ta farko a Bangladesh a ranar 8 ga Maris, a cikin mutane biyu da suka dawo daga Italiya da mace ɗaya.
A ranar 9 ga Maris, an warkar da mutanen uku.
SARS-CoV-2 ya riga ya kamu da mutane sama da miliyan a duniya
Rahoton Jami'ar Johns Hopkins ya nuna cewa jimillar adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar SARS-CoV-2 a duniya sun haura miliyan daya a ranar Alhamis.
Kimanin mutane dubu 52 ne suka mutu sakamakon cutar COVID-19, cutar da ke haifar da kwayar cutar coronavirus.
An sanar da wannan adadi ne a ranar da Malawi ta sanar da kamuwa da cutar korona ta farko da kuma mutuwar farko ta cutar a Zambia.
A ranar Alhamis, Koriya ta Arewa ta bayyana cewa tana daya daga cikin kasashen da suka rage da ba su da cutar coronavirus.
Jiya, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta sanar da cewa an tabbatar da kamuwa da cutar 1,051,635, tare da kamuwa da cutar 79,332 a cikin awanni ashirin da huɗu da suka gabata zuwa 10 na yammacin Turai (08:00 GMT) a ranar 4 ga Afrilu.
A Amurka, an ba da rahoton fiye da mutane 244,000 da suka kamu da cutar coronavirus, tare da mutuwar mutane 5,900.
Bisa ga bayanan Jami'ar Johns Hopkins, CBS News ta ruwaito cewa mutane 1,000 ne suka mutu sakamakon cutar coronavirus a Amurka a ranar Laraba.
A duniya, kasashe sun sanar da tsauraran matakai don hana yaduwar cutar.
A ranar Alhamis, magajin garin Moscow, Sergei Sobyanin, ya tsawaita dokar hana fita zuwa ranar 1 ga Mayu.
