Majalisar dokokin Portugal ta kara wa'adin dokar ta baci na kwanaki 15 a zaben da aka yi, inda aka samu kuri'u 215, 10 suka amince, daya kuma ya ki.
Saudiyya ta kara wa'adin rufewa na birnin Makka da Madina tsawon yini guda, tun daga karfe 3 na yamma zuwa karfe 6 na safe.
